<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٠٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(بمد)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> النبي <span class="special">ﷺ</span> أجزأ عنك، وإن <span class="c2">(أعطيت)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> بالمد الذي <span class="c2">(تقوت)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span> به أهلك أجزأ عنك.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
